author: Jonathan Sawyer
title: Uncovering 5 Unique and Rare Porsche Factory Models
text:
This month Porsche introduces its new Top 5 series on YouTube. The project finds the automobile manufacturer taking a look at some of the rarest Porsche factory models, providing enthusiasts with a “whole new level of sports car history.”
Here we showcase the first episode of Top 5 , centering around the 964 Turbo S, 924 Carrera GTS, 911 GT1, 911 SC/RS and 56 American Roadster.
Press play above to delve into some of Porsche’s rarest models, and stay tuned for the second episode which is expected to highlight the best Porsche sounds.
